> ## Young Cloud Serpent
> *Large dragon, neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 14
> - **Hit Points** 95 (10d10 + 40)
> - **Speed** 30 ft., fly 80 ft.
> ___
> |  STR  |  DEX  |  CON  |  INT  |  WIS  |  CHA  |
> |:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|
> | 8 (-1)|18 (+4)|18 (+4)| 8 (-1)|13 (+1)|12 (+1)|
> ___
> - **Saving Throws** Dex +7, Wis +4, Cha +4
> - **Skills** Acrobatics +7, Perception +4
> - **Damage Immunities** lightning, thunder
> - **Senses** passive Perception 14
> - **Languages** --
> - **Challenge** 6 (2,300 XP)
> ___
> ***Flyby.*** The cloud serpent doesn't provoke opportunity attacks when it flies out of an enemy's reach.
>
> ***Keen Senses.*** The cloud serpent has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight, hearing, or smell.
> 
> ***One With The Storm.*** The cloud serpent is unaffected by strong winds or heavy precipitation.
>
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack.*** The cloud serpent makes three attacks: one with its bite and two with its claws.
> 
> ***Bite.*** *Melee Weapon Attack.* +7 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. *Hit:* 15 (2d10 + 4) piercing damage.
>
> ***Claw.*** *Melee Weapon Attack.* +7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.
> 
> ***Constrict.*** *Melee Weapon Attack.* +7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* 9 (1d10 + 4) bludgeoning damage, and the target is grappled (escape DC 15). Until this grapple ends, the creature is restrained, and the cloud serpent can't constrict another target.
> 
> ***Storm Breath (Recharge 5-6).*** The cloud serpent exhales a lightning storm in a 30-foot cone. Each creature in the cone must make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw, taking 16 (3d10) lightning damage and 16 (3d10) thunder damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature that takes thunder damage must make a DC 15 Constitution save or be deafened for 1 minute.

